title: Homenagem de Desagravo ao Redemptor do Mundo
original_title: Homenagem de Desagravo ao Redemptor do Mundo
body: A single issue of a newspaper published on October 26, 1913 by the Catholic Youth of Funchal, in a large format and with 24 pages.

Funchal: Location where the newspaper was published

Catholic Youth: Responsible for the publication of the newspaper

1913: Year of publication of the newspaper
